    "en": {
      "title": "Gota was not a skilled politician",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Udayanga Weeratunga, the former ambassador of Russia, said that former President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa has said that he will come to Sri Lanka on the 24th.",
        "Mr. Gotabhaya Rajapaksa is not a skilled politician. He also says that he is a competent administrative officer. He also says that Gotabaya is not as talented as Mahinda Rajapaksa as a politician.",
        "Mr. Weeratunga said this in a media inquiry while returning from the Criminal Investigation Department to give a statement regarding the alleged MiG aircraft fraud that took place during the war."
      ],
